{"tid":1470534,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有樣野真係要讚下班警犬，我地要學下","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:23:35.000Z","uid":54303,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6039400f22157a13b3d8d26f8a20cfc2e9df09ec","tid":1470534,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"就係唔割席呀！<br />\n有唔同意見都好，事發時都要死攬到底！<br />\n絕不篤灰、割席、隨便懷疑手足！<br />\n有意見，可以心平氣和、虛心交流，但亂話手足立心不良就係唔得！Be Humble &amp; Trust Your Brothers! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為團結先係我地最大既本錢，香港人今鋪都輸埋就玩撚完架啦。望下西藏新疆咩下場啦！"},{"pid":"86f00d3931d82c6ebf0655bf1e4fb2a24acae78b","tid":1470534,"uid":149630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"打一個對家就嗌晒交<br />\n義士斷晒手腳反而被蓋過<br />\n<br />\n快啲煲大佢<br />\n<br />\n疑遭警方濫用私刑 三十名示威者全部骨折<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470105</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea856a6f155740fc684a5edc05021d5080f63cfd","tid":1470534,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲柒左永遠都係死撐<br />\n然後扮冇野 繼續抹黑<br />\n大家有冇見過元秋上881柒左講人收錢、外國勢力然後去去道歉？<br />\n冇丫嘛！大家學野啦"},{"pid":"b353c1acd19c01bac4eb78ef7edd06377b5093f9","tid":1470534,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"a010bf6fd15854f2319025f8d253936f290f23f3","tid":1470534,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea856a6f155740fc684a5edc05021d5080f63cfd","tid":1470534,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲柒左永遠都係死撐<br />\n然後扮冇野 繼續抹黑<br />\n大家有冇見過元秋上881柒左講人收錢、外國勢力然後去去道歉？<br />\n冇丫嘛！大家學野啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"岩！"},{"pid":"4dee480b690cb64b7e2f64cd9862d0cb72bf78db","tid":1470534